Package: acleddata
Title: Read ACLED Conflict Data from Databricks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Miguel", "Purroy", email = "mpurroyvitola@worldbank.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simple interface to read ACLED (Armed Conflict Location
    and Event Data) from a Databricks Unity Catalog Volume. Requires
    DATABRICKS_HOST and DATABRICKS_TOKEN to be set in ~/.Renviron.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
